{"tid":2183694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大肚婆][831][警謊] 警察疑蓄意襲擊孕婦","createTime":"2020-09-01T05:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T01:07:51.000Z","uid":39808,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"47578c6554c31b464a7bdf082ba7e34d683d3927","tid":2183694,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:39:14.000Z","msg":"襲擊片段<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/i12szt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fi12szt&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7g1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=a53ef7d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/i12szt</a><br />\n<br />\n片段中見到，數名警察發射胡椒噴劑後，驅散了其他人，而孕婦一人坐在地上，一警察從後竄出，先搖了兩下其手持的胡椒噴劑罐，再瞄準向孕婦襲擊射出胡椒噴劑，及後轉身不顧而去，其行動與其他同樣有發射胡椒噴劑的警察有異，似是蓄意襲擊孕婦。<br />\n<br />\n從<em>香港人連儂牆</em>的直播影片中（約21:00開始）可見，那幫拘捕男子的警察，在拘捕並製造混亂前就已知現場孕婦所在，而非警方聲稱的&quot;及後發現&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rmsCuST.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrmsCuST.jpg&h=81cd9ba9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n襲擊孕婦片段來源<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=403846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D403846&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7g1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=3c6b8d4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D403846&h=561fbe6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=403846</a><br />\n香港人連儂牆直播影片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKPictureig/videos/766619437425858/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKPictureig%2Fvideos%2F766619437425858%2F&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7g1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=e1d1492c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKPictureig/videos/766619437425858/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9EX643h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%